Hedrick Smith, journalist and 
author of "Who Stole the American Dream" discusses reasons for 
the decline of the middle class. Smith talks with Bloomberg's 
Pimm Fox and  Carol Massar  on Bloomberg Radio's "Taking Stock" on
September 9th.    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 12:25
 